      "id": "peshitta:first-corinthians.3.20",
      "translationId": "peshitta",
      "bookSlug": "first-corinthians",
      "chapterNumber": 3,
      "verseNumber": 20,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Corinthians 3:20",
      "text": "ܘܬܘܒ ܡܪܝܐ ܝܕܥ ܡܚܫܒܬܗܘܢ ܕܚܟܝܡܐ ܕܤܪܝܩܢ ܐܢܝܢ ܀",
